üí° Pro tip for ICS/OT:
Treat your cybersecurity policies like your physical safety SOPs.
If you wouldn‚Äôt hand a new operator an untested procedure for a high-pressure chemical valve, don‚Äôt hand them an untested cybersecurity procedure either. The principle is the same: clarity, education, and enforceability save lives and systems.
